                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The Path River Peeler gains the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened] condition or its frightened condition increases</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The Peeler Strides or Climbs up to its Speed. The Peeler gains a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against reactions triggered by this movement.</p>"
